<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>商品頁｜SENWEI</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <img src="/assets/logo.jpg" alt="SENWEI logo">
          <span class="brand-name">SENWEI</span>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="/" data-nav>首頁</a>
          <a href="/about" data-nav>關於我們</a>
          <a href="/product" data-nav>商品頁</a>
          <a href="/passport" data-nav>商品護照</a>
          <a href="/admin" data-nav>登入</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <% 
        function normalizeAssetUrl(v) {
          if (!v || typeof v !== 'string') return '';
          var s = v.trim();
          if (!s) return '';
          if (/^https?:\/\//i.test(s)) return s;
          if (s.startsWith('/public/')) return '/' + s.slice('/public/'.length);
          if (s.startsWith('public/')) return '/' + s.slice('public/'.length);
          if (s.startsWith('/')) return s;
          return '/' + s;
        }
        const productImg = normalizeAssetUrl(hero && hero.hero_image_path) || '/assets/product-illustration.svg';
      %>
      <section class="page-hero center">
        <div class="container">
          <span class="eyebrow"><%= hero.eyebrow %></span>
          <h1><%- hero.title %></h1>
          <p><%= hero.description %></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container product-showcase">
          <div class="product-panel image">
            <img src="<%= productImg %>" alt="森維修護潤澤精華乳產品視覺" />
          </div>
          <div class="product-panel copy">
            <div class="inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">SENWEI Signature</span>
              <h2>森維修護潤澤精華乳</h2>
              <p>
                為熟齡肌膚設計的溫和修護系列，強調舒緩乾燥、提升柔潤感與穩定膚況。包裝與說明同樣以銀髮友善為前提，讓每日保養更輕鬆、更安心。
              </p>
              <div class="badge-list" style="justify-content:center;">
                <span class="badge">低刺激膚感</span>
                <span class="badge">清楚標示</span>
                <span class="badge">環境友善故事</span>
              </div>
              <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/passport">查詢商品護照</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section highlight">
        <div class="container card-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>質地感受</h3>
            <p>輕柔延展、容易推開，適合熟齡肌膚每日保養時使用，減少拉扯與負擔感。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>使用體驗</h3>
            <p>包裝操作與產品說明以直覺為主，讓長者或照護者都能更容易理解與使用。</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>透明資訊</h3>
            <p>透過商品護照頁面，未來可延伸查看批次、檢測摘要與產品永續資訊。</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <div>
          <div class="tagline">SENWEI</div>
          <small>銀髮友善護膚品牌｜環境友善保養理念</small>
        </div>
        <small>網站製作：來就補多媒體行銷</small>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>

